WEBVTT

00:06:27.792 --> 00:06:30.886
RM: Facebook is the greatest
advertizing platform ever invented.

00:06:31.363 --> 00:06:34.898
My sense is that Facebook
provides any marketer

00:06:34.922 --> 00:06:41.025
with targeting that is better
and more cost-effective

00:06:41.049 --> 00:06:43.023
than anything that ever preceded it.

00:06:43.047 --> 00:06:45.285
There's a reason
why the stock's done so well.

00:06:45.309 --> 00:06:47.452
And there's a reason
why I was such a big fan.

00:06:47.476 --> 00:06:49.872
It seemed to be something
that didn't hurt anybody.

00:06:49.896 --> 00:06:52.963
The problem here, Chris,
and I think the issue with the Russians,

00:06:52.987 --> 00:06:56.492
is that the way the incentives work --
and this is not a Facebook issue,

00:06:56.516 --> 00:06:59.142
this is the Valley and candidly,
the whole US economy --

00:06:59.166 --> 00:07:01.031
which, there really weren't any rules.